	(4,'2016-12-14 14:04:15','2016-12-14 13:59:51','health','foraging','life','[]',3,'bontonstory','WILD PEAR EXTRACT / RECIPE / FOOD PHOTOGRAPHY','11.050 SBD',0,'<html>\n<p><img src=\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15439889_1869296400023848_2396800600303445211_n.jpg?oh=c4925f2a66887dd9db4750b57caa1650&amp;oe=58B55235\" width=\"900\" height=\"500\"/></p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15578609_1869296456690509_8247000210610525595_n.jpg?oh=aeb3adbc4f03f1f3bcd6510d7e896c05&amp;oe=58EE41F0\" width=\"640\" height=\"960\"/></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h1>Wild Pear!</h1>\n<p>This is my wild pear juice. I enjoy drinking a mild juice, so I mix pear extract with lots of water. The wild pear is a fruit of Pyrus montana Nakai according to Korean Medicine Dictionary. Natural wild pear is less sweet and sour than normal pears. Enjoy with some honey. I drink because wild pear is good for cough and diarrhea. However, wild pear has more good effects to our body. It is helpful for weak lungs, and it helps to clean blood. I believe that it will be so helpful for my health during winter.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15492599_1869296490023839_1623901914744036493_n.jpg?oh=a44e1f859fd68f11490f716225d14646&amp;oe=58E7A267\" width=\"900\" height=\"500\"/></p>\n<p>Image source of wild pear tree: minsada,tistory</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15541151_1869296636690491_1395357334559511345_n.jpg?oh=ad35438c020f43b2c63824b6a2457177&amp;oe=58F6F0F0\" width=\"900\" height=\"500\"/></p>\n<h1>Wash wild pears and slice them!</h1>\n<p>To make wild pear extract, boil sliced pears over medium-low heat for a long time. Squeeze them well by your own way. I use a kind of fabric cooking bag. If you have jujubes, add them too. The taste will be more sweet and helpful for the prevention of colds. It is not difficult to make, you just need your little patience to wait to finish.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15421001_1869296553357166_1080250250621537601_n.jpg?oh=a8bbf434c5c67f53a2bf57daf6be0b0d&amp;oe=58E99F5A\" width=\"640\" height=\"960\"/></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>@bontonstory</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15232253_1855580511395437_2927404053905043409_n.jpg?oh=bca52f9a5403f7d49ee7baea3ba88d28&amp;oe=58B52B2B\" width=\"900\" height=\"19\"/></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15193603_1859175504369271_1599007493561458341_n.jpg?oh=6d8781c1b8ec57bf8d0e30ecc9ca3edb&amp;oe=58F1F51E\" width=\"900\" height=\"500\"/></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15171016_1854237688196386_4470743484022751398_n.jpg?oh=273f9b7efac9dfc3845039f9b1bd140a&amp;oe=58ED50CE\" width=\"900\" height=\"400\"/></p>\n</html>','{\"tags\":[\"food\",\"health\",\"foraging\",\"life\"],\"users\":[\"bontonstory\"],\"image\":[\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15439889_1869296400023848_2396800600303445211_n.jpg?oh=c4925f2a66887dd9db4750b57caa1650&oe=58B55235\",\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15578609_1869296456690509_8247000210610525595_n.jpg?oh=aeb3adbc4f03f1f3bcd6510d7e896c05&oe=58EE41F0\",\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15492599_1869296490023839_1623901914744036493_n.jpg?oh=a44e1f859fd68f11490f716225d14646&oe=58E7A267\",\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15541151_1869296636690491_1395357334559511345_n.jpg?oh=ad35438c020f43b2c63824b6a2457177&oe=58F6F0F0\",\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15421001_1869296553357166_1080250250621537601_n.jpg?oh=a8bbf434c5c67f53a2bf57daf6be0b0d&oe=58E99F5A\",\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15232253_1855580511395437_2927404053905043409_n.jpg?oh=bca52f9a5403f7d49ee7baea3ba88d28&oe=58B52B2B\",\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15193603_1859175504369271_1599007493561458341_n.jpg?oh=6d8781c1b8ec57bf8d0e30ecc9ca3edb&oe=58F1F51E\",\"https://scontent-icn1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15171016_1854237688196386_4470743484022751398_n.jpg?oh=273f9b7efac9dfc3845039f9b1bd140a&oe=58ED50CE\"],\"app\":\"steemit/0.1\",\"format\":\"html\"}','steem','[\"karenmckersie\",\"drac59\",\"drac59\"]','wild-pear-extract-recipe-food-photography','SBD','food'),
