	(11,'2016-12-14 14:04:51','2016-12-14 08:49:00','challenge','service','christ','lighttheworld',0,'gavvet','December 14th - material materialism','38.769 SBD',0,'Our wardrobes fill up, but what about those who have no wardrobe and nothing to put in one as they only have the clothes on their backs.\n-\nIts cold out there or new threads might help land a job.\n\nThe modern world is steadily losing basic skills, could we make our own clothing if things went from bad to worse?\n\n\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yKiuhCkiV5E\n\nThis is the fourteenth way of serving in 25 ways over 25 days leading up to Christmas.\n-\nIts easy:\n\n1. watch the short clip\n2. follow the instructions\n3. make it happen\n4. then tweet or otherwise share your results using... #lighttheworld... encourage others to participate\n5. 25 days is enough consistency to form a new habit...\n\nIf every day this December we are slightly more mindful of others we may find ourselves with a new great habit to continue into the new year and beyond.\n-\n>THREE SIMPLE WAYS TO GET INVOLVED\n\n>- [Learn from a wise king](https://www.lds.org/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.14-27?lang=eng#13) how we should love those in need.\n>- Collect winter clothing (old or new) for your local homeless shelter.\n>- Recently purchased some new clothes? Donate some old ones to a charity or thrift store.\n\n>OTHER WAYS TO PARTICIPATE\n\n>- Learn some basic sewing skills or help someone else to do the same.\n>- Invite your children to go through their clothing and identify two complete outfits that can be donated to a thrift store.\n>- Knit a cap for a newborn baby and donate it to your local hospital.\n>- Buy hand warmers and give them to people working (or living) outside in the cold.\n>- Visit JustServe.org for more ways to #LIGHTtheWORLD in your community (U.S. and Canada only).\n\nMore detail and the embedded links can be found directly from this link\n-\nhttps://www.mormon.org/christmas/in-25-ways-over-25-days/jesus-taught-us-to-clothe-the-naked\n\nShout out to @elyaque for his cool badges... try some.\nhttp://i1024.photobucket.com/albums/y301/gavvet/curationorca_zpst6yiuyl6.jpg','{\"tags\":[\"christmas\",\"challenge\",\"service\",\"christ\",\"lighttheworld\"],\"image\":[\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/yKiuhCkiV5E/0.jpg\",\"http://i1024.photobucket.com/albums/y301/gavvet/curationorca_zpst6yiuyl6.jpg\"],\"links\":[\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yKiuhCkiV5E\",\"https://www.lds.org/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.14-27?lang=eng#13\",\"https://www.mormon.org/christmas/in-25-ways-over-25-days/jesus-taught-us-to-clothe-the-naked\"],\"app\":\"steemit/0.1\",\"format\":\"markdown\",\"users\":[\"elyaque\"]}','steem','[]','december-14th-material-materialism','SBD','christmas'),
