	(81,'2016-12-14 17:43:24','2016-12-14 17:43:24','money','story','funny','gambling',4,'scan0017','Quento and Craig go traveling #2','0.055 SBD',0,'When is the last time you felt so thoroughly disappointed in one particular event that you thought your night was crushed...  Only to rise from the ashes like a Phoenix screaming towards the heavens?\nThis happened to Quento and I in New Orleans.\nHere is our story:\nAfter an amazing dinner the previous night, we ventured into the Harrah\'s casino a few blocks away from Bourbon Street:\n[![IMG_1298.jpg](https://s29.postimg.org/wm2s2ye8n/IMG_1298.jpg)](https://postimg.org/image/morr9w6mr/)\nWe checked out the Diamond Lounge for drinks and to see what food they offered...\n[![IMG_1277.jpg](https://s29.postimg.org/7cy0oah47/IMG_1277.jpg)](https://postimg.org/image/ynjbw7k0z/)\nNOT BAD!\nEspecially when the food and beverages (Old Fashionds) cost only tips!\n[![IMG_1275.jpg](https://s27.postimg.org/dnaa22w03/IMG_1275.jpg)](https://postimg.org/image/lg0xu21z3/)\nDelicious, luck-inspiring, the lounge was amazing.\n[![IMG_1279.jpg](https://s27.postimg.org/h0yi1wfoj/IMG_1279.jpg)](https://postimg.org/image/ejmqumvrz/)\nNext stop!?!\nHonoring the freebies by gambling like silly goose!  (Mystery) solved!  THAT\'S why the libations come free...  AMAZING!\nQuento went to sort out cash from a cash machine (you\'re nearly guaranteed to get money out of those), while I sat down at a fun looking slot machine.\nSad story, happy ending:\nMy math wasn\'t quite on when we did the calculations...  Played all lines, maximum bet.\nResult?  Won zero, spent $50 on that one pull.\n(Face palm).  Thoroughly disheartened, got up, Quento nowhere to be seen, decided, what the heck?  Play all lines, minimum bet.  $10 a pull...  Pretty rich pull!  He knows where to find me, so I\'ll play S L O W L Y.\nTiming is everything!  Reels were in the midst of spinning when Quento returned!\nThe result?\n[![IMG_1281.jpg](https://s23.postimg.org/r031dd38r/IMG_1281.jpg)](https://postimg.org/image/jk3rrkfjb/)\nBig bonus!\nYay!!!\n[![IMG_1286.jpg](https://s27.postimg.org/xqrub6pz7/IMG_1286.jpg)](https://postimg.org/image/4bm626lfj/)\n[![IMG_1287.jpg](https://s23.postimg.org/xz0dcpegr/IMG_1287.jpg)](https://postimg.org/image/m9wdoqnhz/)\nBANG!\nThe result:\n[![IMG_1288.jpg](https://s24.postimg.org/ufhu0zsol/IMG_1288.jpg)](https://postimg.org/image/59gvu5re9/)\nWe took off from there like we were chasing the last chopper out of \'Nam.\nHappy ending, good times!!!\nWe both wish everyone the same luck!!!','{\"tags\":[\"travel\",\"money\",\"story\",\"funny\",\"gambling\"],\"image\":[\"https://s29.postimg.org/wm2s2ye8n/IMG_1298.jpg\",\"https://s29.postimg.org/7cy0oah47/IMG_1277.jpg\",\"https://s27.postimg.org/dnaa22w03/IMG_1275.jpg\",\"https://s27.postimg.org/h0yi1wfoj/IMG_1279.jpg\",\"https://s23.postimg.org/r031dd38r/IMG_1281.jpg\",\"https://s27.postimg.org/xqrub6pz7/IMG_1286.jpg\",\"https://s23.postimg.org/xz0dcpegr/IMG_1287.jpg\",\"https://s24.postimg.org/ufhu0zsol/IMG_1288.jpg\"],\"links\":[\"https://postimg.org/image/morr9w6mr/\",\"https://postimg.org/image/ynjbw7k0z/\",\"https://postimg.org/image/lg0xu21z3/\",\"https://postimg.org/image/ejmqumvrz/\",\"https://postimg.org/image/jk3rrkfjb/\",\"https://postimg.org/image/4bm626lfj/\",\"https://postimg.org/image/m9wdoqnhz/\",\"https://postimg.org/image/59gvu5re9/\"],\"app\":\"steemit/0.1\",\"format\":\"markdown\"}','steem','[\"scan0017\",\"sindy\",\"sergey44\",\"adelja\"]','quento-and-craig-go-traveling-2','SBD','travel'),
	(82,'2016-12-14 17:43:33','2016-12-14 17:43:33','creative','writers','spanish','life',15,'betamusic','Sin amor, sin el mar /  Without love, without the sea  (Un Poema Original / An Original Poem)','0.546 SBD',1,'<img src=\"http://www.poemas-romanticos.info/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/FRENTE-AL-MAR-e1362102482220.jpg\" alt=\"FRENTE-AL-MAR-e1362102482220.jpg\">\n\n<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.poemas-romanticos.info/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/FRENTE-AL-MAR-e1362102482220.jpg\" rel=\"noopener\">Fuente de la Imagen / Image Source </a></blockquote>\n \nCuando la aurora me agarre despierta y acongojada\nCuando el sentir se apague\nCuando tu piel no vea\nCuando pierda los animos\nCuando ya no te sienta\n\nQue voy a hacer cuando ya no te tenga?\nCuando mire a mi lado y no te vea\nCuando las persona pregunten por ti\nY mi ser pierda fortaleza?\n\nQue voy a hacer sin ti amor\nSin amor, sin el mar\nSin el aire, sin poder volar\nQue será de mi corazón \ntan acostumbrado al tuyo\ntan sensible y tosudo\n\nQue me depara el destino?\nUn silencio total?\nUn clandestino desierto?\nSin amor sin el mar.\nSin el aire, sin poder volar\n\nComparto con ustedes, este poema, que escribí hace poco, como lo han notado, no escribo muy bien en Ingles, es por ello, que mis poemas, solamente los escribo en Español, de igual manera, le permito a cualquier stemians, que desee traducirlo a cualquier idioma, publicarlo en su blog y conservar su recompensa.\n\nGracias por su atencion!.\n\n<blockquote>Share with yours, this poem, that wrote makes little, as it have noticed, not write very well in English, is by this, that my poems, only them write in Spanish, of equal way, you allow to any stemians, that want to translate it to any language, publish it in your blog and keep your rewards.\n\nThank you for your attention!.</blockquote>','{\"tags\":[\"poetry\",\"creative\",\"writers\",\"spanish\",\"life\"],\"image\":[\"http://www.poemas-romanticos.info/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/FRENTE-AL-MAR-e1362102482220.jpg\"],\"links\":[\"http://www.poemas-romanticos.info/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/FRENTE-AL-MAR-e1362102482220.jpg\"],\"app\":\"steemit/0.1\",\"format\":\"markdown\"}','steem','[\"betamusic\",\"sindy\",\"sergey44\",\"aidancloquell\",\"mallorcaman\",\"estibuil\",\"mokluc\",\"selwi\",\"pavelmenme\",\"peterz\",\"jamesbrown\",\"solidsnake\",\"wormhole\",\"adelja\",\"carlos-cabeza\"]','sin-amor-sin-el-mar-without-love-without-the-sea-un-poema-original-an-original-poem','SBD','poetry'),
