	(135,'2016-12-15 10:10:57','2016-12-15 09:38:06','life','writing','philosophy','[]',4,'mdog','The Great Sun (An original poem)','0.002 SBD',0,'<html>\n<p>https://s23.postimg.org/wspiz4iob/4428518_sunrise_wallpapers.jpg</p>\n<h2>The Great Sun</h2>\n<p>Oh, great sun! Come morning,</p>\n<p>shines its light to awaken us.</p>\n<p>It brings joy to a boring day</p>\n<p>by showering us with its powerful rays.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Its bright smile and its golden face,</p>\n<p>giving life to every place.</p>\n<p>It paints the rose gardens red,</p>\n<p>while kids play on the hill up ahead.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Hours passed, its energy is running low</p>\n<p>for it must recharge and sleep while plants grow.</p>\n<p>How beautiful is its sunset,</p>\n<p>with hints of orange, it\'s as beautiful as it can get.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>At night time, the sun is finally asleep</p>\n<p>since its energy it must keep.</p>\n<p>It will wake up in the morning, after a while</p>\n<p>feeling all refreshed with another great big smile.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We thank the sun for making our lives so fantastic,</p>\n<p>because life without the sun would be tragic.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Thank you for reading, I hope you enjoyed it!</strong></p>\n<p>Image Sources: <a href=\"http://7-themes.com/collections/sunrise-wallpapers/\">1</a></p>\n</html>','{\"tags\":[\"poetry\",\"life\",\"writing\",\"philosophy\"],\"image\":[\"https://s23.postimg.org/wspiz4iob/4428518_sunrise_wallpapers.jpg\"],\"links\":[\"http://7-themes.com/collections/sunrise-wallpapers/\"],\"app\":\"steemit/0.1\",\"format\":\"html\"}','steem','[\"dixonloveart\",\"edgarsart\",\"herverisson\",\"drac59\"]','the-great-sun-an-original-poem','SBD','poetry'),
